DatabaseModel.Description: DB project for the main funcions of bank application.

Table.Name: account
Table.Description: Base account info. Passwords stores in SHA-512 hash.

Table.Name: city
Table.Description: Possible cities in relation to countries.

Table.Name: account_consents
Table.Description: Association table between client and consents (marketing ect..).

Table.Name: activity_log
Table.Description: Sub-session category, client activity on account.

Table.Name: action_type
Table.Description: Action types of activity on account.

Table.Name: preferred_contact
Table.Description: How to contact with client account.
